No communication,

00:44:17.976 --> 00:44:22.798
write it down again on the
corner of your notepad what

00:44:22.798 --> 00:44:27.980
you're going to do.
Don't communicate you guys;

00:44:27.980 --> 00:44:34.685
show your neighbor.
