00:44:34.685 --> 00:44:37.333
again, so ready.
Without cheating,

00:44:37.333 --> 00:44:42.531
without looking around you,
if you invested--let Jude get a

00:44:42.531 --> 00:44:47.640
good view of you--if you
invested raise your hand now.

00:44:47.640 --> 00:44:52.533
If you didn't invest--okay.
All right, can I look at the

00:44:52.533 --> 00:44:55.389
