00:44:59.179 --> 00:45:04.550
Let's do it again,
third time, hang on a second.

00:45:04.550 --> 00:45:08.264
So third time,
write it down,

00:45:08.264 --> 00:45:14.990
and pretend this is real cash.
Now, if you invested the third

00:45:14.990 --> 00:45:19.253
time raise your hand.
There's a few suckers born

00:45:19.253 --> 00:45:23.659
everyday but basically.
So, where are we heading here?

00:45:23.659 --> 00:45:26.349
Where are we heading pretty
rapidly?

00:45:26.349 --> 00:45:29.039
We're heading towards an
equilibrium;

00:45:29.039 --> 00:45:30.920
let's just make sure we confirm
that.

00:45:30.920 --> 00:45:33.748
So everyone who didn't invest
that third time raise your

00:45:33.748 --> 00:45:35.250
hands.
