equilibrium which is bad.

00:51:00.989 --> 00:51:03.729
Prisoner's Dilemma has the bad
equilibrium when nobody tidies

00:51:03.729 --> 00:51:06.469
their room or both guys go to
jail, but I claim this is not a

00:51:06.469 --> 00:51:10.239
Prisoner's Dilemma.
Get the guy behind you.

00:51:10.239 --> 00:51:13.980
Student: No one suffered
