00:51:13.980 --> 00:51:15.470
Professor Ben Polak:
Okay, so maybe the outcome isn't

00:51:15.470 --> 00:51:16.811
quite so bad.
That's fair enough,

00:51:16.811 --> 00:51:19.747
I could have made it worse,
I could have made it sort of--I

00:51:19.747 --> 00:51:22.733
could have made that--I could
have lowered the payoffs until

00:51:22.733 --> 00:51:24.730
they were pretty bad.
Why else is this not a

00:51:24.730 --> 00:51:27.719
Prisoner's Dilemma?
The woman who's behind you.

00:51:27.719 --> 00:51:29.670
Student: Because there's
